<item>
            <title>[LU-676] Select machinefile option for mpirun via a variable </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-676</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Not all MPI implementations pass the host file to mpirun via the same&lt;br/&gt;
option. Common options are -machinefile and -hostfile. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This problem can be resolved by using a variable MACHINEFILE_OPTION&lt;br/&gt;
instead. A default value is assigned if the variable not defined.&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
                <environment>1.8.6 servers running centos5.6 and 1.8.6 clients running sles11sp1.</environment>
